text: Ridgeway is an unincorporated community (Class Code U6) in Winona County, Minnesota. It is at latitude 43.912 and longitude -91.56 (Ridgeway Panoramio Photos). The elevation is 1,342 feet. Ridgeway is on the Witoka U.S. Geological Survey Map. ==Sources== ==Other websites== *GNIS Map of Ridgeway Category:Unincorporated communities in Minnesota
title: Ridgeway, Minnesota
